'''证书颁发机构安全理事会'''（{{lang|en|'''The Certificate Authority Security Council'''}}，缩写'''CASC'''）也称'''证书颁发机构理事会'''，是由多个行业供应商[[倡导团体|倡导团体]]创建的进行研究、促进{{tsl|en|Internet security|互联网安全}}标准和教育公众对待互联网安全问题的组织。

== 历史 ==
该组织由最大的七家[[数字证书认证机构|数字证书颁发机构]]、[[電子證書|SSL证书]]颁发者成立于2013年2月，它们是：[[科摩多集团|科摩多集团]]（Comodo）、[[赛门铁克|赛门铁克]]（Symantec）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.symantec.com/connect/blogs/let-s-build-more-secure-future |title=Let’s Build a More Secure Future {{!}} Symantec Connect Community |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2017-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927160330/https://www.symantec.com/connect/blogs/let-s-build-more-secure-future |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[趨勢科技|趨勢科技]]（Trend Micro）、[[DigiCert|DigiCert]]、[[Entrust|Entrust]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.entrust.com/news/2013-02-14-Entrust-Joins-Worlds-Leading-CAs-to-Form-Certificate-Authority-Security-Council-Advance-Internet-Security-and-Trusted-SSL-Ecosystem |title=Entrust Joins World's Leading CAs to Form Certificate Authority Security Council, Advance Internet Security and Trusted SSL Ecosystem - Feb 14, 2013 |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2019-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924181800/https://www.entrustdatacard.com/about/newsroom/overview |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[GlobalSign|GlobalSign]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thepaypers.com/news/e-identity-security-online-fraud/globalsign-joins-the-certificate-authority-security-council-to-upgrade-internet-security/750211-26 |title=The Paypers. |access-date=2017-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702184430/http://www.thepaypers.com/news/e-identity-security-online-fraud/globalsign-joins-the-certificate-authority-security-council-to-upgrade-internet-security/750211-26 |archive-date=2015-07-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>和[[GoDaddy|GoDaddy]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://inside.godaddy.com/announcing-certificate-authority-security-council/ |title=Announcing the Certificate Authority Security Council {{!}} Inside GoDaddy.com |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2013-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111090725/http://inside.godaddy.com/announcing-certificate-authority-security-council/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="autogenerated1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.darkreading.com/authentication/167901072/security/news/240148546/major-certificate-authorities-unite-in-the-name-of-ssl-security.html |title=Major Certificate Authorities Unite In The Name Of SSL Security - Dark Reading |access-date=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2013-04-10 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130410174711/http://www.darkreading.com/authentication/167901072/security/news/240148546/major-certificate-authorities-unite-in-the-name-of-ssl-security.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.networkworld.com/news/2013/021413-council-digital-certificate-266728.html |title=Multivendor power council formed to address digital certificate issues - Network World |access-date=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2013-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728114851/http://www.networkworld.com/news/2013/021413-council-digital-certificate-266728.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cmswire.com/cms/customer-experience/website-certificate-authorities-set-up-security-council-for-advocacy-research-019619.php |title=Website Certificate Authorities Set Up Security Council for Advocacy, Research |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2017-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927113512/http://www.cmswire.com/cms/customer-experience/website-certificate-authorities-set-up-security-council-for-advocacy-research-019619.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://electronicstaff.com/2013/ssl-certificate-authority-security-council-takes-root |title=SSL Certificate Authority Security Council Takes Root {{!}} Electronic Staff |access-date=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714155147/http://electronicstaff.com/2013/ssl-certificate-authority-security-council-takes-root |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 目标 ==
CASC支持[[CA/浏览器论坛|CA/浏览器论坛]]和其他标准制定机构的成果。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://casecurity.org/casc/ |title=About the CA Security Council |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2017-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714183658/https://casecurity.org/casc/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>它们支持改进[[傳輸層安全協議|安全套接字层]]（SSL）和[[数字证书认证机构|数字证书颁发机构]]（CA）运作的增强开发。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://casecurity.org/2013/02/14/worlds-leading-certificate-authorities-come-together-to-advance-internet-security-and-the-trusted-ssl-ecosystem/ |title=CA Security Council {{!}} World’s Leading Certificate Authorities Come Together to Advance Internet Security and the Trusted SSL Ecosystem |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2016-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827200441/https://casecurity.org/2013/02/14/worlds-leading-certificate-authorities-come-together-to-advance-internet-security-and-the-trusted-ssl-ecosystem/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.networkworld.com/news/2013/021513-certificate-authorities-band-together-to-266752.html |title=Certificate authorities band together to boost security - Network World |access-date=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2014-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140225002025/http://www.networkworld.com/news/2013/021513-certificate-authorities-band-together-to-266752.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

根据Comodo [[CTO|CTO]]及理事会成员Robin Alden，CASC将作为所有CA的统一战线：“虽然不是一个标准制定组织，我们致力于提供有关SSL的[[最佳实践|最佳实践]]和用法的教育、研究和宣传来补充标准制定组织。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://threatpost.com/en_us/blogs/cas-form-new-alliance-focus-security-issues-education-021413 |title=CAs Form New Alliance to Focus on Security Issues, Education {{!}} threatpost |access-date=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2013-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130308133506/http://threatpost.com/en_us/blogs/cas-form-new-alliance-focus-security-issues-education-021413 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 会员要求 ==
CASC的会员要求为满足其信誉、操作和安全性要求的SSL证书颁发机构。会员必须接受年度审计，并遵守行业标准，例如CA/浏览器论坛的基线要求和网络安全指南。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://casecurity.org/casc/ |title=CA Security Council {{!}} About the CA Security Council |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2017-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714183658/https://casecurity.org/casc/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 行业倡导 ==
该组织协作创建和定义各项举措，以提高对政策及其对互联网基础设施影响的理解。

=== 证书撤销和OCSP装订 ===
该组织的焦点之一是促进对证书撤销检查重要性以及[[OCSP装订|OCSP装订]]好处的理解。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.techworld.com/security/3426528/new-certificate-authorities-group-promises-better-revocation-checking/ |title=New Certificate Authorities group promises better revocation checking - Techworld.com |access-date=2017-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201203901/http://news.techworld.com/security/3426528/new-certificate-authorities-group-promises-better-revocation-checking/ |archive-date=2014-02-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>该协议旨在确保Web用户在访问SSL证书已被撤销或过期的网站时了解这点。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9236803/Certificate_Authorities_to_push_for_better_certificate_revocation_checking?taxonomyId=245 |title=Certificate Authorities to push for better certificate-revocation checking - Computerworld |accessdate=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2014-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202182549/http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9236803/Certificate_Authorities_to_push_for_better_certificate_revocation_checking?taxonomyId=245 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 使用数字代码签名保护软件分发 ===
该组织还致力于通过数字[[代码签名|代码签名]]实现安全的软件分发。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.eweek.com/security/code-signing-seen-as-effective-way-to-safeguard-app-security.html|title=Code Signing Seen as Effective Way to Safeguard App Security|last=Kerner|first=Sean Michael|publisher=eWeek}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=CA Security Council和微软公司在保护在线用户方面提出新标准|url=https://www.sslchina.com/leading-certificate-authorities-and-microsoft-introduce-new-standards-to-protect-consumers-online/|website=SSL中国|accessdate=2017-02-09|date=2016-12-14|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211080424/https://www.sslchina.com/leading-certificate-authorities-and-microsoft-introduce-new-standards-to-protect-consumers-online/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=沃通代码签名证书升级公告|url=http://www.wosign.com/news/2017-0126-01.htm|website=沃通|accessdate=2017-02-09|date=2017-01-26|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211075702/http://www.wosign.com/news/2017-0126-01.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=通知： GlobalSign 标准型代码签名证书产品升级|url=http://cn.globalsign.com/company/news-1045.html|website=GlobalSign|accessdate=2017-02-09|date=2017-01-13}}</ref>代码签名证书有助用户识别软件代码来自真实的有信誉的发布者，并在确保代码接收未被篡改方面发挥关键作用。

